oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Original wills, Achtzehner, Frank, 1860 May 07
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: An original will of Frank Achtzehner, dated May 7th, 1860. Illustrates the first page of the document; the original is written in German. Achtzehner’s will was presented for probate to the Davidson County Court on October 13th, 1866. Forms part of Record Group 16, Original Wills, 1780-1925.
